The **[mountain resort transportation Colorado](https://expresscoloradotransportation.com/colorado-mountain-resort-transportation/)** services that excel understand these microclimates intuitively. For example, the corridor between Denver and Summit County experiences what meteorologists call "orographic lifting," where air masses rising over mountains create unpredictable weather patterns. I've recorded temperature variations of 20 degrees Fahrenheit within 10 miles on the same highway.

